{
  "description": "Cristian always shows up to give his best. He is a great friend, trustworthy, always willing to recommend others to roles or projects.

Not many people know this but he's also a very successful creator in the traditional fashion industry on Instagram.

Knows a lot about marketing, would recommend him as an advisor or contractor any day"
}

{
  "description": "I was onboarded to Claynosaurz through Andrew and recently discovered his spaces & podcasts. A unique mind that shares a lot of insight whilst remaining down to earth and personable. Trusted figure in the space."
}

{
  "description": "Really like Lau. He puts in the effort and is reliable. Classic web3 grinder that you want in your circle / group. Very friendly and eager to help"
}

{
  "description": "I was feeling a bit stuck in my own web3 bubble and wanted to join some new groups  that’s how I ended up discovering the Gorilla community through your group. I had already seen your videos, so I decided to join, and it’s been a great decision so far. The people are amazing  always good conversations, solid calls, and they truly live and breathe web3. I’m really glad I got to know them!"
}

{"description":"So happy to finally meet the Abstract Chain family IRL 🫶
I’ve been seeing sillybilly’s posts on Twitter for so long, and gotta say — his content is always on point: clear, thoughtful, and makes Abstract Chain even easier to love 💚

So glad to have new friends in Thailand! I’ll be back soon — fish dinner with you and Nat is a must! 🐟"}

{"description":"From the very first day at Abstract Chain, Duck has been helping the Chinese community grow — answering questions, sharing updates, and keeping everyone informed about every move in the Abstract ecosystem.

His posts are always great, and he’s incredibly responsible and patient. 💚

Honestly, without Duck, the Chinese community wouldn’t be nearly as organized. Thank you 鸭鸭！💚"}

{
  "description": "I met Meow during KBW in Korea while participated in Abstract and Pudgy Penguin events. Once I got to talk to her and we exchanged our twitters, she is one of a few that told me she saw my content before while showing her appreciation to this contribution toward Abstract\n\nthis is something really small but means a lot especially to those who're contributing to any community out there. since we've been joining many events there and met her couple times, I could say that she is the one who truly cares to surrounded people"
}
